      "text": "Topic: Wavelength."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 10160.0,
      "end_time": 12580.0,
      "text": "Why red is used as a danger signal?"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 12599.0,
      "end_time": 13599.0,
      "text": "Well."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 13600.0,
      "end_time": 14780.0,
      "text": "Because my teacher said so."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 14780.0,
      "end_time": 17740.0,
      "text": "As usual, you are wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 17740.0,
      "end_time": 21820.0,
      "text": "The major reason for red to be used as a danger signal is its wavelength."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 22840.0,
      "end_time": 24179.0,
      "text": "I know."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 24180.0,
      "end_time": 26440.0,
      "text": "Wavelength is the distance between two sea waves."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 26560.0,
      "end_time": 27560.0,
      "text": "No."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 27940.0,
      "end_time": 29300.0,
      "text": "In the wave theory of light."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 29300.0,
      "end_time": 33480.0,
      "text": "The distance between successive crests or troughs is called wavelength."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 34060.0,
      "end_time": 37120.0,
      "text": "Longer the wavelength, lesser will be the scattering of light."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 37940.0,
      "end_time": 42760.0,
      "text": "Now, among the colors of visible light, red has the longest wavelength."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 42760.0,
      "end_time": 47100.0,
      "text": "Hence, it is least scattered by the atmospheric particles."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 47100.0,
      "end_time": 52620.0,
      "text": "As a result, whether it is fog or smoke, red light passes comparatively easily through them."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 54320.0,
      "end_time": 60420.0,
      "text": "Thus, it can be seen from maximum distance, making red color the right choice to convey any danger."
    },
